import React, { useContext } from 'react' import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom' import { UserContext } from '../../../context/user-context' import './Navlinks.scss' const Navlinks = (props) => { const { isLoggedIn } = useContext(UserContext) return (
  • All Users
  • My Places
  • Add Place
  • {!isLoggedIn ? Authenticate : Authenticate }
) } export default Navlinks
